casebody.data:
NORTHERN TRUST CORPORATION, et al., Petitioners,
v.
Lindie L. BANKS, et al. No. 19-440 Supreme Court of the United States. Feb. 24, 2020

Motion of American Bankers Association, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied.
